            'iab_notice_description' => '<p>Thina kanye <button id="cnzIABNoticeButton" class="cnz-iab-dec-btn" aria-label="partners">{vendor_count} ozakwethu</button> sisebenzisa amakhukhi nobuchwepheshe bokulandela umkhondo ukuthuthukisa umuzwa wakho kuwebhusayithi yethu. Singase sigcine futhi/noma sifinyelele ulwazi kudivayisi futhi sicubungule idatha yomuntu siqu, njengekheli lakho le-IP nedatha yokuphequlula, ukuze sithole ukukhangisa nokuqukethwe okwenziwe kwaba ngokwakho, ukukhangisa nokulinganisa okuqukethwe, ucwaningo lwezithameli nokuthuthukiswa kwamasevisi. Ukwengeza, singase sisebenzise idatha enembile yendawo kanye nokuhlonza ngokuthwebula idivayisi.</p><p>Sicela uqaphele ukuthi imvume yakho izosebenza kuwo wonke ama-subdomain ethu. Ungashintsha noma uhoxise imvume yakho nganoma yisiphi isikhathi ngokuchofoza inkinobho ethi "Izintandokazi Zemvume" ezansi kwesikrini sakho. Siyazihlonipha izinqumo zakho futhi sizibophezele ekukunikezeni umuzwa wokuphequlula obala novikelekile.</p>',
            'iab_preference_description' => '<p>Yenza izintandokazi zakho zemvume ngokwezifiso zezigaba zamakhukhi nezintandokazi zokulandela umkhondo zokukhangisa zezinjongo nezici nabathengisi abangezansi. Unganikeza imvume enemininingwane yombili <button id="cnzIABPreferenceButton" class="cnz-iab-dec-btn" aria-label="Third Party Vendor">Umthengisi Wenkampani Yangaphandle</button> kanye <button id="cnzIABGACMPreferenceButton" class="cnz-iab-dec-btn" aria-label="Google Ad Tech Provider">Umhlinzeki Wezobuchwepheshe Bokukhangisa we-Google</button>. Abathengisi abaningi badinga imvume yokucubungula idatha yomuntu siqu, kuyilapho abanye bethembele esithakazelweni esisemthethweni. Noma kunjalo, unelungelo lokuphikisa ukusetshenziswa kwabo kwesithakazelo esisemthethweni.</p>',
